       fhir:description [ fhir:v "As a <a href=\"ActorDefinition-EIRstaffORhealthworker.html\">EIR staff OR health worker</a>, I want:\n>To be able to manually flag duplicate vaccination events\n\nso that\n\n>I can report duplicates that the system was not able to identify" ] ;
